name: Temple Jump - Prepare to Fall Edition

description:
This is a difficult Platformer game that is meant to frustrate you and create some tension

Have fun playing it :)

It will have updates in the future (big one in april 2020) so follow my itch.io page.

This is my second all-by-me game made  with the godot engine.
